name: Breast Squeeze / Elbow Squeeze Variation LoRA
description:
This is my Breast Squeeze LoRA, with the variation that the breasts are squeezed by the elbows. This LoRA is trained on NovelAI, so it will not do particularly well with realistic models.

The strength is good from 0.6 to 0.8, but I use 0.75 strength. All images are generated are generated with Hires Fix and the Orangemix VAE. All pictures were made with the blends available on my profile.

The keywords are 'elbow squeeze', and 'breasts squeezed together'. This LoRA has two types of generations. If you add in 'arms up', then the arms will be folded upwards. If you add 'arms down', then the arms will be folded downwards.

I also have a Discord. Join if you wanna share results, get advice, or make requests.
